title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 22 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 22 2021
description:
Mumbling, forgetful Joe Biden's predictably calamitous CNN town hall. Buck says those who once supported Biden should be "ashamed." Biden shows his disdain and basically calls the unvaccinated murderers. NBA's Enes Kanter, who Clay says knows all too well what having freedom withheld is, doubles down on China criticism. SCOTUS will hear challenge to Texas abortion law. State challenges may mean big abortion law changes lie ahead.
